    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure schools get additional staff and facilities for in school covid testing",
        "additional_details": "Most schools will not have the staff capacity or facilities to make this idea a reality. It is vital that this testing initiative is successful hence staffing and facilities must be provided.",
        "background": "The government announced that in January schools will need to facilitate rapid testing for pupils and staff. This is a positive step in reducing transmission and is likely to be welcomed by most staff. I believe for this to be effective additional staff and facilities will be needed.",
